name: changeAddress

testSteps.description: Given that I'm logged in to HR space as 'Kathrine Alkjaersig Vad'

children.description: Given that I'm logged in to HR space using 'A186795' account

testSteps.description: When i click tile: My Profile
When i go to address
When i click on portlet edit button: Address
When i populate effective date: 10/12/2022
When i populate address type: Mailing
When i populate country in address: Switzerland
When i populate only for employees under swiss contract: Yes
When i populate address line 1: LYInzijvwLg
When i populate address line 2: TCxuCnBFItl
When i populate address line 3: WyYVyAHJegs
When i populate postal code: 1949
When i populate town: TOWN
When i populate county: Bern
When i click save button
When i click proceed button
When i populate text area field: CH COMMENT
When i check workflow participant: HR Admin for CH
When i click confirm button
Then the pending request label is displayed: Addresses change pending approval
Given that I'm logged in to HR space as 'Domer DIMAYACYAC'
When i click approval request tile: Review and Approve
Then the value in address fields are reflected for approval: LYInzijvwLg, TCxuCnBFItl, WyYVyAHJegs, 1949, TOWN, Bern, Switzerland
When i populate text area field: HR ADMIN COMMENT
When i click post button
Then the value is reflected in activity portlet: HR ADMIN COMMENT
When i click approve button
Given that I'm logged in to HR space as 'Kathrine Alkjaersig Vad'
When i click tile: My Profile
When i go to address
Then the updated field is displayed in address portlet: LYInzijvwLg, TCxuCnBFItl, WyYVyAHJegs, 1949, TOWN, Bern, Switzerland
